{"tid":848479,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【讀書好】轉山走河 - 劉細良太平紳士","createTime":"2018-10-05T03:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T03:18:13.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0e34d1c8091034a850a9d38c7ff4d654ecce1038","tid":848479,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"我是書評人，也是作者，或因政論為人認識，但寫得最多其實是旅遊，由十多年前的《大朝聖》、《帶着偏見去旅行》到《過客》系列及《森羅萬象》，平均三年出版一本。寫旅遊比政論難，因為香港政客水平實在低，每天題材手到拿來，三扒兩撥就可落鑊上碟奉客，但旅遊人人都是專家，各有所好，手機世代有片有真相，可即時景點現場直播，還等閣下旅行回來，慢慢用文字記錄旅途上的感受？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/article/20181005/20514761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F20514761&d=%2Bmo84QD1zui%2BOBj9n2G7cx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=6370c7f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F20514761&h=0223f552\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/article/20181005/20514761</a>"}]}